description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Beginner Bodyweight Circuit ' from the channel Rina Thomas.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Progression Quest vibe.
The The Foundation Builder vibe means Strengthen weak points, rebuild, perfect the basics. This is especially good for Those coming back from injury or refining fundamentals. The The Progression Quest vibe means Methodical, incremental, long-term improvement. This is especially good for Anyone who loves tracking progress and leveling up..
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Beginner whole body focus off Hydrow and 90-second intervals on Hydrow.

Max rhythm: 24, Format: EMOM...
